==English==

===Noun===
'''wittol'''  
# a man who knows of his wife's adultery but puts up with it, a ''contented [[cuckold]]''.

===References===
* ''God help the husband that obliges his wife's least whim: he'll be a wittol ere he's two years wed!'' — [[w:John Barth|John Barth]], "The Sot-Weed Factor".

